sistant Referees (VAR)", "keywords": [], "long_description": "The role of the VAR is to assist the referee to determine whether there was an infringement that means a goal should not be awarded. As the ball has crossed the line, play is interrupted so there is no direct impact on the game.\n\n-The referee informs the VAR, or the VAR recommends to the referee that a decision/incident should be reviewed.\n\n-The video footage is reviewed by the VAR, who advises the referee via headset what the video shows.", "short_description": "In this simulation, you will be the video assistant referees inside football match"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://vargame.online/privacy-policy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "8 owl studio", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://vargame.online/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8708246299213556"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974468_987274533209454_2934793964009576115_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=-MJYWSUa30YQ7kNvgG69M1r&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDmnj4J7wgogiVnKQv37HEl1T09VJcY9fA75mXAbtHSDg&oe=6724A8F0"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "Video Assistant Referees (VAR)", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "context_ca